---
layout: base.njk
title: "Finance Calculator Tools"
description: "Free finance calculators: tip calculator, percentage calculator, loan and EMI calculator. No signup required."
canonical: "https://everyday-tools.pages.dev/finance/"
---

<div class="container">
  <nav class="breadcrumb" aria-label="Breadcrumb">
    <a href="/">Home</a> &rsaquo; Finance Tools
  </nav>

  <h1>Finance Calculator Tools</h1>
  <p class="category-intro">Free financial calculators to help with everyday money decisions. All calculations happen instantly in your browser — no data is sent anywhere.</p>

  <div class="tool-list">
    {%- for tool in tools -%}
      {%- if tool.category == "finance" -%}
        <div class="tool-card">
          <h2><a href="/finance/{{ tool.slug }}/">{{ tool.name }}</a></h2>
          <p>{{ tool.description }}</p>
          <a class="tool-link" href="/finance/{{ tool.slug }}/">Open {{ tool.name }} &rarr;</a>
        </div>
      {%- endif -%}
    {%- endfor -%}
  </div>
</div>
